name: HOMUNC (person person)
description:
An original Gory Orgy animated loop. 12 seconds. 1228X1228, H264, 2021
HOMUNC is a multi-layered animation that utilises more than one machine-learning model. A fleshy, shape-shifting homunculus (computer generated nude) is conspicuously analysed by a machine-learning model that identifies people and objects. HOMUNC (person person) is one of 10. One copy is retained by the artist, while the other 9 are available for purchase. Gory Orgy is the experimental machine-learning project by kiwi artist and film-maker Ed Lust.
